---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<BaseLayout title="纽约大学 | 李卓衡" description="NYU - Master of Management & Analytics">
  <h1 class="page-title">
    <span class="content-zh">纽约大学</span>
    <span class="content-en">New York University</span>
  </h1>
  <p class="page-subtitle content-zh">管理与管理分析硕士（商业分析）· 2025.09 – 2026.12（预计）· GPA 3.83/4.00</p>
  <p class="page-subtitle content-en">M.S. in Management & Analytics (Business Analytics) · 2025.09 – 2026.12 (Expected) · GPA 3.83/4.00</p>

  <div class="edu-page-body">
    <div class="content-zh">
      <p>此处可填写纽约大学就读经历、校园生活、课程与项目等文字。您可上传照片后替换下方占位区域。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content-en">
      <p>Add your NYU experience, campus life, courses and projects here. Replace the placeholder below with your photos.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="edu-media-placeholder">
    <span class="content-zh">照片与文字待上传</span>
    <span class="content-en">Photos & text to be added</span>
  </div>

  <p class="page-footer"><a href={base}>← <span data-i18n="navHome">首页</span></a></p>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-title { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .page-subtitle { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }
  .edu-page-body p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .edu-media-placeholder {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 200px;
    background: rgba(22, 27, 34, 0.22);
    backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass-blur));
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass-blur));
    border: 1px dashed var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--glass-shadow);
  }
  .page-footer { margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); }
</style>
